enumDescription: Possible error codes that could be returned by CustomerUserError.

values.name: BAD_DOMAIN
values.description: Input email contains an invalid domain name.

values.name: PASSWORD_STARTS_OR_ENDS_WITH_WHITESPACE
values.description: Input password starts or ends with whitespace.

values.name: TAKEN
values.description: The input value is already taken.

values.name: TOO_LONG
values.description: The input value is too long.

values.name: TOO_SHORT
values.description: The input value is too short.
